image_analysis.description: A photograph of a closet containing three white wire mesh drawer units stacked with various office supplies and books. On top of the units are several books, including 'TOEFL iBT' and 'Fire and Fury'. The drawers are labeled with white tape. A blue garment hangs on a rod to the right. A pair of white slippers is on the floor in front of the units.
